data.description: Don't miss this great house located in New Castle, close to the interstate and shopping areas. This home was built on the Jefferson floor plan which includes two walk in closets in the master and crown molding throughout. This home includes a nice and open floor plan, tall ceilings, two closets in the master suite and no carpert in the entire home. The kitchen is well equipped with kitchen aid appliances, plenty of counter space, island with eating bar, built in cabinets and a pantry, equipped with a sprinkler system and generator hookup.  Fresh paint inside with a nice size backyard that would be great for entertaining and kids to gather and play. You can't beat this square footage for this price. Schedule your showing today!
